sj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` | Project context, architecture diagram, tech stack |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` | AR-009 detailed proposal for Router module |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | AR-008 delta spec (Sandbox GC) -- format reference |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md` | Session routing specification (most relevant to router) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md` | Session routing design (detailed code-level design for `pkg/router`) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Sandbox orchestration design (types, APIs, constants) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` | Sandbox orchestration specification |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md` | Session store design (Redis/Valkey) |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` | Helm chart, Dockerfiles, Makefile targets |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` | SDD prompt with client-go API reference for AR-009 |\n\n---\n\n### 3. Router-Related Code and Directories\n\n**No `pkg/router` directory exists yet.** However, there is extensive design and specification for it:\n\n**AR-009 Change Request** (the current task):\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-009/proposal.md` -- Contains TODO placeholders\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-009/design.md` -- Contains TODO placeholders\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-009/tasks.md` -- Contains TODO placeholder\n\n**The `session-routing/` directory contains the most detailed router design:**\n\nFrom `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md`, the planned `pkg/router` package structure includes:\n\n```go\n// Config\ntype Config struct {\n    Port                  string\n    Debug                 bool\n    EnableTLS             bool\n    TLSCert               string\n    TLSKey                string\n    MaxConcurrentRequests int\n}\n\n// Server struct\ntype Server struct {\n    config         *Config\n    engine         *gin.Engine\n    httpServer     *http.Server\n    sessionManager SessionManager\n    storeClient    store.Store\n    httpTransport  *http.Transport\n    jwtManager     *JWTManager\n}\n\n// SessionManager interface\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n\n// JWTManager\ntype JWTManager struct {\n    privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n    publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n    clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n}\n```\n\n**Route table:**\n\n| Method | Path | Handler |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| GET | `/health/live` | `handleHealthLive` |\n| GET | `/health/ready` | `handleHealthReady` |\n| GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n| GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n\n---\n\n### 4. Existing Delta-Spec and Spec Files\n\n**Root-level delta-spec:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- AR-008 (Sandbox GC), serves as format reference\n\n**Per-change delta-specs:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-007/delta-spec.md`\n\n**No `delta-spec.md` exists in AR-009 yet** -- this is what needs to be created.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Configuration Files\n\n**`go.mod`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`):\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\ngo 1.25.0\n\nKey dependencies:\n- github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0\n- github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0\n- github.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.22.0\n- k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n- k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n- k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1\n- sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n```\n\n**Makefile targets relevant to router:**\n- `build_router` -- builds `./cmd/router`\n- `run_router` -- `go run ./cmd/router/main.go --port=8080 --debug`\n- `docker-build-router` -- builds `agentcube-router:latest`\n- `docker-buildx-push-router` -- multi-arch push\n\n**Dockerfile for router** (`docker/Dockerfile.router`):\n- Builder: `golang:1.24.9-alpine`, copies `client-go/`, builds `./cmd/router`\n- Runtime: `alpine:3.19`, user `router` UID 1000, CMD `[\"--port=8080\", \"--debug\"]`\n\n---\n\n### 6. \"Router HTTP 反向代理核心\" Feature Documentation\n\nThe feature is tracked as **AR-009**. Here is what is known:\n\n**From `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`:**\n\n**Purpose:** Build a Go-based HTTP reverse proxy core module (`pkg/router`) to route external HTTP requests to internal AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter service instances. Serves as the traffic entry point for the agentcube system.\n\n**In Scope:**\n1. Core reverse proxy engine based on `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy`\n2. Route rule management (path/Host-based matching, dynamic registration via CRDs)\n3. Service discovery via client-go Informer mechanism (watching AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD changes)\n4. Load balancing (Round-Robin, Least-Connections, health checks)\n5. Middleware support (logging, trace ID injection, auth, rate limiting)\n\n**Out of Scope:** TLS cert management, advanced traffic governance (canary, A/B testing), WebSocket/gRPC support.\n\n**Proposed directory structure:**\n```\npkg/router/\n|-- router.go          # Router interface and core implementation\n|-- proxy.go           # ReverseProxy wrapper\n|-- backend.go         # Backend management and health checks\n|-- loadbalancer.go    # Load balancing strategies\n|-- middleware.go      # Middleware (logging, tracing, rate limiting)\n|-- informer.go        # CRD Informer integration\n|-- config.go          # Config struct\n|-- router_test.go     # Unit tests\n```\n\n**Core interface design:**\n```go\ntype Router interface {\n    AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n    RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n    ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n}\n\ntype Backend struct {\n    URL      *url.URL\n    Weight   int\n    Healthy  bool\n}\n```\n\n**From `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md` (key requirements):**\n\n- Session resolution from `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n- Reverse proxy to sandbox using `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints`\n- JWT injection (RS256, RSA 2048-bit) for sandbox kinds\n- Forwarding headers (`X-Forwarded-Host`, `X-Forwarded-Proto`, `X-Forwarded-For`)\n- Proxy error mapping (connection refused -> 502, timeout -> 504)\n- Concurrency limiting with semaphore middleware (default 1000)\n- Health endpoints (`/health/live`, `/health/ready`)\n- h2c/http2 support, ReadTimeout 30s, IdleTimeout 90s\n\n**From `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md` (key implementation details):**\n\n- JWT constants: `rsaKeySize = 2048`, `jwtExpiration = 5 * time.Minute`, `IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"`\n- Environment variables: `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` (required), `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` (optional, default \"default\")\n- Dependencies: gin, golang-jwt/jwt/v5, golang.org/x/net/http2, k8s.io packages, `pkg/store`, `pkg/common/types`, `pkg/api`\n\n**Key types from `pkg/common/types` (used by router):**\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n    SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n    Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n    EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n    SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n}\n\ntype SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n    Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n    Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n    Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n}\n\ntype CreateSandboxResponse struct {\n    SessionID   string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxID   string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    SandboxName string              `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    EntryPoints []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary of What the Router Module Should Implement\n\nBased on all the gathered documentation, the `pkg/router` module needs to implement:\n\n1. **HTTP Server** (Gin-based) with health endpoints and invocation routes for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n2. **Session Manager** that resolves sessions from Redis/Valkey store, creates sandboxes via WorkloadManager HTTP API\n3. **Reverse Proxy** using `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` that forwards requests to sandbox pods based on `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints`\n4. **JWT Manager** (RS256, RSA 2048-bit) for signing outbound requests to sandboxes, with K8s Secret-based key persistence\n5. **Concurrency Middleware** (semaphore-based, default 1000 concurrent requests)\n6. **CRD Informer Integration** for dynamic service discovery (watching AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter changes)\n7. **Configuration** via CLI flags and environment variables\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28888a50bffeHDgHNOoKMQeQSH","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775825804016,"end":1775825949141}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775825949208,"sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","part":{"id":"prt_d777991d80019cg7v1pOrGnpfl","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d77773b89001fVXfA6QIdZTzAb","sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":19575,"input":19232,"output":239,"reasoning":104,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.005874325}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775825951509,"sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","part":{"id":"prt_d77799b12001IXXBXcKntioakF","messageID":"msg_d7779922d001MjH1hob0AsoMLW","sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775825953666,"sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","part":{"id":"prt_d77799f4c00198NqTugf0udMpd","messageID":"msg_d7779922d001MjH1hob0AsoMLW","sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_93d020494a224fbcb13c1861","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 增强 `pkg/workloadmanager/handler` 中已有的 `LifecycleManager` GC 循环，新增四项缺失的垃圾回收能力：(1) 基于空闲超时的 sandbox 清理，(2) 孤立 CR（Orphan CR）扫描与删除，(3) 幽灵 Store 条目（Ghost Entry）扫描与清理，(4) GC Prometheus 指标暴露。同时将 GC 路径中的 `log.Printf` 替换为结构化日志 `slog`。本变更是对 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的补充，确保 sandbox 资源不会因状态不一致而泄漏。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: SandboxInfo 新增 LastActivityAt 字段\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `handler/models.go` 的 `SandboxInfo` 结构体中新增 `LastActivityAt time.Time` 字段，JSON tag 为 `lastActivityAt`。零值表示该 sandbox 不纳入空闲超时检查，回退到 TTL 过期逻辑。Sandbox 创建时 `LastActivityAt` SHALL 初始化为 `CreatedAt`。\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: LastActivityAt 初始化为 CreatedAt\n14: \n15: - **GIVEN** 新的 sandbox 正在创建\n16: - **WHEN** `SandboxInfo` 被构造\n17: - **THEN** `LastActivityAt` 被设置为与 `CreatedAt` 相同的值\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: LastActivityAt 为零值时回退到 TTL\n20: \n21: - **GIVEN** 某 sandbox 的 `LastActivityAt` 为零值（`time.Time{}`）\n22: - **WHEN** GC 循环评估该 sandbox 是否过期\n23: - **THEN** 跳过空闲超时检查，使用 `CreatedAt + defaultTTL` 判断是否过期\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ### Requirement: LifecycleManagerDeps 新增 GC 配置字段\n28: \n29: The system SHALL 在 `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` 的 `LifecycleManagerDeps` 结构体中新增以下字段：\n30: - `DefaultIdleTimeout time.Duration` — 默认空闲超时，默认值 15 分钟\n31: - `MaxOrphanScanLimit int` — 单次孤儿扫描最大 CR 数量，默认值 100\n32: - `MetricsRecorder GCMetrics` — GC 指标记录器，可选（nil 时禁用指标）\n33: \n34: 构造函数 `NewLifecycleManager(deps)` SHALL 对未显式配置的字段应用默认值：`DefaultIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`，`MaxOrphanScanLimit = 100`。\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: 默认值填充\n37: \n38: - **GIVEN** `LifecycleManagerDeps` 中 `DefaultIdleTimeout` 和 `MaxOrphanScanLimit` 均为零值\n39: - **WHEN** `NewLifecycleManager(deps)` 被调用\n40: - **THEN** `DefaultIdleTimeout` 设为 15 分钟，`MaxOrphanScanLimit` 设为 100\n41: \n42: #### Scenario: 显式配置覆盖默认值\n43: \n44: - **GIVEN** `LifecycleManagerDeps` 中 `DefaultIdleTimeout = 30 * time.Minute`，`MaxOrphanScanLimit = 200`\n45: - **WHEN** `NewLifecycleManager(deps)` 被调用\n46: - **THEN** 使用传入值，不覆盖\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: MetricsRecorder 为 nil 时不 panic\n49: \n50: - **GIVEN** `MetricsRecorder` 为 nil\n51: - **WHEN** GC 循环执行完成\n52: - **THEN** 指标记录被跳过，不 panic\n53: \n54: ---\n55: \n56: ### Requirement: GC 循环执行顺序\n57: \n58: The system SHALL 在每次 GC tick 中按以下顺序串行执行子任务：\n59: 1. TTL 过期清理（已有逻辑，增强指标和日志）\n60: 2. 空闲超时清理（新增）\n61: 3. 孤立 CR 扫描（新增）\n62: 4. 幽灵 Store 条目扫描（新增）\n63: 5. 记录周期摘要日志和指标（新增）\n64: \n65: 任一子任务发生错误 SHALL 不中断后续子任务的执行，错误被记录并计入指标后继续。\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: 子任务错误不阻断后续任务\n68: \n69: - **GIVEN** TTL 过期清理子任务因 K8s API 错误失败\n70: - **WHEN** GC 循环执行\n71: - **THEN** 错误被记录和计数，空闲超时清理子任务仍然执行\n72: \n73: #### Scenario: 所有子任务依次执行\n74: \n75: - **GIVEN** GC tick 触发，所有子任务均正常\n76: - **WHEN** GC 循环执行\n77: - **THEN** 按 TTL → 空闲 → 孤儿 → 幽灵 → 摘要的顺序依次完成\n78: \n79: ---\n80: \n81: ### Requirement: 空闲超时清理\n82: \n83: The system SHALL 在 GC 循环中遍历 Store 中所有 `Status = \"running\"` 的 sandbox，对每个 sandbox 执行空闲超时检查：\n84: 1. 若 `LastActivityAt` 为零值，跳过该 sandbox（由 TTL 逻辑处理）\n85: 2. 读取 sandbox 对应 CR 的 `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` annotation\n86: 3. 若 annotation 不存在或无法解析，使用 `DefaultIdleTimeout`（15 分钟）\n87: 4. 若 `time.Now().After(LastActivityAt + idleTimeout)`，标记为过期并删除\n88: 5. 删除操作：先删除 K8s CR，再从 Store 移除条目\n89: \n90: `Status = \"pending\"` 的 sandbox SHALL 不参与空闲超时检查（仍在初始化中）。\n91: \n92: #### Scenario: Sandbox 超过空闲超时被删除\n93: \n94: - **GIVEN** sandbox `sess-001` 状态为 `running`，`LastActivityAt` 为 20 分钟前，空闲超时为 15 分钟\n95: - **WHEN** GC 空闲清理子任务执行\n96: - **THEN** 该 sandbox 的 K8s CR 被删除\n97: - **AND** Store 中对应条目被移除\n98: - **AND** `IncCleanupTotal(\"idle\")` 被调用\n99: \n100: #### Scenario: Sandbox 在空闲超时窗口内被保留\n101: \n102: - **GIVEN** sandbox `sess-002` 状态为 `running`，`LastActivityAt` 为 5 分钟前，空闲超时为 15 分钟\n103: - **WHEN** GC 空闲清理子任务执行\n104: - **THEN** 该 sandbox 不被删除，Store 条目保持不变\n105: \n106: #### Scenario: 使用 CR annotation 中的 per-sandbox 空闲超时\n107: \n108: - **GIVEN** sandbox `sess-003` 的 CR 携带 annotation `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout: \"30m\"`\n109: - **AND** `LastActivityAt` 为 20 分钟前\n110: - **WHEN** GC 空闲清理子任务执行\n111: - **THEN** 使用 30 分钟作为阈值，sandbox 不被删除\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: Pending 状态 sandbox 不参与空闲清理\n114: \n115: - **GIVEN** sandbox `sess-004` 状态为 `pending`，`LastActivityAt` 为 30 分钟前\n116: - **WHEN** GC 空闲清理子任务执行\n117: - **THEN** 该 sandbox 不被空闲超时逻辑删除\n118: \n119: #### Scenario: annotation 无法解析时使用默认值\n120: \n121: - **GIVEN** sandbox CR 的 `runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout` annotation 值为 `\"invalid\"`\n122: - **WHEN** GC 解析该 annotation\n123: - **THEN** 使用 `DefaultIdleTimeout`（15 分钟）作为阈值\n124: \n125: ---\n126: \n127: ### Requirement: 孤立 CR 扫描与删除\n128: \n129: The system SHALL 在 GC 循环中扫描 Kubernetes 集群中携带 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` label 的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CR，检测并删除那些在 Store 中没有对应条目的孤立 CR：\n130: 1. 使用 dynamic client 列出所有 AgentRuntime CR（带 session-id label），限制 `MaxOrphanScanLimit` 条\n131: 2. 使用 dynamic client 列出所有 CodeInterpreter CR（带 session-id label），限制 `MaxOrphanScanLimit` 条\n132: 3. 对每个 CR，提取 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` label 值\n133: 4. 调用 `Store.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` 检查 Store 中是否存在对应条目\n134: 5. 若不存在，删除该 CR\n135: 6. 记录 `IncCleanupTotal(\"orphan_cr\")`\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: 孤立 AgentRuntime CR 被删除\n138: \n139: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime-abc123` 携带 label `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-orphan-1`\n140: - **AND** Store 中不存在 `sess-orphan-1` 条目\n141: - **WHEN** GC 孤儿扫描子任务执行\n142: - **THEN** 该 CR 被从 K8s 集群删除\n143: - **AND** `IncCleanupTotal(\"orphan_cr\")` 被调用\n144: \n145: #### Scenario: 有 Store 条目的 CR 被保留\n146: \n147: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime-def456` 携带 label `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-active-1`\n148: - **AND** Store 中存在 `sess-active-1` 条目\n149: - **WHEN** GC 孤儿扫描子任务执行\n150: - **THEN** 该 CR 不被删除\n151: \n152: #### Scenario: 孤立 CodeInterpreter CR 被删除\n153: \n154: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter CR `default/my-ci-ghi789` 携带 label `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-orphan-2`\n155: - **AND** Store 中不存在 `sess-orphan-2` 条目\n156: - **WHEN** GC 孤儿扫描子任务执行\n157: - **THEN** 该 CR 被从 K8s 集群删除\n158: \n159: #### Scenario: 扫描数量受 MaxOrphanScanLimit 限制\n160: \n161: - **GIVEN** 集群中有 150 个携带 session-id label 的 CR\n162: - **AND** `MaxOrphanScanLimit` 为 100\n163: - **WHEN** GC 孤儿扫描子任务执行\n164: - **THEN** 本轮只扫描前 100 个 CR，剩余 50 个在后续 GC 周期中扫描\n165: \n166: ---\n167: \n168: ### Requirement: 幽灵 Store 条目扫描与清理\n169: \n170: The system SHALL 在 GC 循环中遍历 Store 中的所有 sandbox 条目，检测并清理那些在 Kubernetes 集群中对应 CR 已不存在的幽灵条目：\n171: 1. 调用 `Store.ListSandboxes(ctx)` 获取所有 Store 条目\n172: 2. 对每个条目，根据其 `Kind`、`Namespace`、`SandboxName` 通过 dynamic client 检查对应 CR 是否存在\n173: 3. 若 CR 不存在（`IsNotFound`），从 Store 中删除该条目\n174: 4. 记录 `IncCleanupTotal(\"ghost_entry\")`\n175: \n176: #### Scenario: 幽灵 Store 条目被清理\n177: \n178: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在条目 `sess-ghost-1`，`Kind = \"AgentRuntime\"`，`Namespace = \"default\"`，`SandboxName = \"my-runtime-xyz\"`\n179: - **AND** K8s 集群中不存在对应的 AgentRuntime CR\n180: - **WHEN** GC 幽灵扫描子任务执行\n181: - **THEN** 该 Store 条目被删除\n182: - **AND** `IncCleanupTotal(\"ghost_entry\")` 被调用\n183: \n184: #### Scenario: 有效 sandbox 条目被保留\n185: \n186: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在条目 `sess-valid-1`\n187: - **AND** 对应的 K8s CR 存在\n188: - **WHEN** GC 幽灵扫描子任务执行\n189: - **THEN** 该 Store 条目不被删除\n190: \n191: #### Scenario: 两种 Kind 的幽灵条目均被清理\n192: \n193: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在一个 AgentRuntime 幽灵条目和一个 CodeInterpreter 幽灵条目\n194: - **WHEN** GC 幽灵扫描子任务执行\n195: - **THEN** 两个幽灵条目均被删除\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ### Requirement: GCMetrics 接口与 Prometheus 指标\n200: \n201: The system SHALL 定义 `GCMetrics` 接口，包含以下方法：\n202: - `IncCleanupTotal(reason string)` — 清理计数，label `reason`（`\"ttl_expired\"` / `\"idle\"` / `\"orphan_cr\"` / `\"ghost_entry\"`）\n203: - `ObserveCleanupDuration(seconds float64)` — 记录单次 GC 周期总耗时\n204: - `IncCleanupErrors(reason string)` — 错误计数，label `reason`\n205: \n206: Prometheus 指标名称 SHALL 为：\n207: - `agentcube_gc_cleanup_total`（Counter，label `reason`）\n208: - `agentcube_gc_cleanup_duration_seconds`（Histogram，buckets: [1, 5, 10, 30, 60, 120, 300]）\n209: - `agentcube_gc_cleanup_errors_total`（Counter，label `reason`）\n210: \n211: #### Scenario: TTL 清理计数\n212: \n213: - **GIVEN** GC 删除了一个 TTL 过期的 sandbox\n214: - **WHEN** 指标被记录\n215: - **THEN** `IncCleanupTotal(\"ttl_expired\")` 被调用\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: 空闲清理计数\n218: \n219: - **GIVEN** GC 删除了一个空闲超时的 sandbox\n220: - **WHEN** 指标被记录\n221: - **THEN** `IncCleanupTotal(\"idle\")` 被调用\n222: \n223: #### Scenario: 孤儿 CR 清理计数\n224: \n225: - **GIVEN** GC 删除了一个孤立 CR\n226: - **WHEN** 指标被记录\n227: - **THEN** `IncCleanupTotal(\"orphan_cr\")` 被调用\n228: \n229: #### Scenario: 幽灵条目清理计数\n230: \n231: - **GIVEN** GC 清理了一个幽灵 Store 条目\n232: - **WHEN** 指标被记录\n233: - **THEN** `IncCleanupTotal(\"ghost_entry\")` 被调用\n234: \n235: #### Scenario: GC 周期耗时被记录\n236: \n237: - **GIVEN** 一个 GC 周期完成，总耗时 3.5 秒\n238: - **WHEN** 周期结束\n239: - **THEN** `ObserveCleanupDuration(3.5)` 被调用\n240: \n241: #### Scenario: 删除错误被计数\n242: \n243: - **GIVEN** GC 删除 sandbox 时 K8s API 返回错误\n244: - **WHEN** 错误被捕获\n245: - **THEN** `IncCleanupErrors(\"delete_failed\")` 被调用\n246: \n247: ---\n248: \n249: ### Requirement: 结构化日志（slog）\n250: \n251: The system SHALL 将 `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` 中所有 `log.Printf` 调用替换为 Go 标准库 `slog` 的结构化日志。日志级别和事件类型 SHALL 遵循以下规范：\n252: \n253: | 事件 | 级别 | 必需字段 |\n254: |------|------|----------|\n255: | GC 周期开始 | `INFO` | `event=\"gc_cycle_start\"`, `check_interval`, `default_ttl`, `default_idle_timeout` |\n256: | Sandbox 被删除 | `INFO` | `event=\"sandbox_deleted\"`, `session_id`, `sandbox_name`, `namespace`, `kind`, `reason` |\n257: | GC 子任务错误 | `ERROR` | `event=\"gc_error\"`, `sub_task`, `error` |\n258: | GC 周期完成 | `INFO` | `event=\"gc_cycle_complete\"`, `duration_ms`, `ttl_cleaned`, `idle_cleaned`, `orphan_cleaned`, `ghost_cleaned`, `errors` |\n259: | 孤立 CR 被删除 | `INFO` | `event=\"orphan_cr_deleted\"`, `session_id`, `cr_name`, `namespace`, `kind` |\n260: | 幽灵条目被清理 | `INFO` | `event=\"ghost_entry_cleaned\"`, `session_id`, `sandbox_name`, `kind` |\n261: \n262: #### Scenario: GC 周期开始日志\n263: \n264: - **GIVEN** GC 循环启动新周期\n265: - **WHEN** 周期开始执行\n266: - **THEN** 一条 `slog.Info` 日志被发出，包含 `event=\"gc_cycle_start\"` 和配置字段\n267: \n268: #### Scenario: Sandbox 删除日志\n269: \n270: - **GIVEN** sandbox `sess-001` 因空闲超时被删除\n271: - **WHEN** 删除操作完成\n272: - **THEN** 一条 `slog.Info` 日志被发出，包含 `event=\"sandbox_deleted\"`, `session_id=\"sess-001\"`, `reason=\"idle\"`\n273: \n274: #### Scenario: GC 错误日志\n275: \n276: - **GIVEN** 孤儿扫描子任务中 List CR 失败\n277: - **WHEN** 错误被捕获\n278: - **THEN** 一条 `slog.Error` 日志被发出，包含 `event=\"gc_error\"`, `sub_task=\"orphan_scan\"`, `error=<错误信息>`\n279: \n280: #### Scenario: GC 周期完成摘要日志\n281: \n282: - **GIVEN** GC 周期完成，本轮清理了 2 个 TTL 过期、1 个空闲超时、0 个孤儿、1 个幽灵，发生 0 个错误，耗时 1500ms\n283: - **WHEN** 周期结束\n284: - **THEN** 一条 `slog.Info` 日志被发出，包含 `event=\"gc_cycle_complete\"`, `duration_ms=1500`, `ttl_cleaned=2`, `idle_cleaned=1`, `orphan_cleaned=0`, `ghost_cleaned=1`, `errors=0`\n285: \n286: ---\n287: \n288: ### Requirement: isExpired 方法增强\n289: \n290: The system SHALL 修改 `LifecycleManager.isExpired(info *SandboxInfo, now time.Time) bool` 方法，使其在判断 TTL 过期时同时考虑 `ExpiresAt` 和 `CreatedAt + defaultTTL`（保持现有行为不变），该方法仅用于 TTL 过期检查，空闲超时检查由独立的 `isIdleExpired` 方法处理。\n291: \n292: #### Scenario: ExpiresAt 已设置时优先使用\n293: \n294: - **GIVEN** sandbox 的 `ExpiresAt` 为非零值且 `now >= ExpiresAt`\n295: - **WHEN** `isExpired(info, now)` 被调用\n296: - **THEN** 返回 `true`\n297: \n298: #### Scenario: ExpiresAt 未设置时使用 CreatedAt + TTL\n299: \n300: - **GIVEN** sandbox 的 `ExpiresAt` 为零值，`CreatedAt` 为 10 小时前，`defaultTTL` 为 8 小时\n301: - **WHEN** `isExpired(info, now)` 被调用\n302: - **THEN** 返回 `true`\n303: \n304: #### Scenario: 未过期返回 false\n305: \n306: - **GIVEN** sandbox 的 `CreatedAt` 为 2 小时前，`defaultTTL` 为 8 小时\n307: - **WHEN** `isExpired(info, now)` 被调用\n308: - **THEN** 返回 `false`\n309: \n310: ---\n311: \n312: ### Requirement: isIdleExpired 新方法\n313: \n314: The system SHALL 在 `LifecycleManager` 中新增 `isIdleExpired(info *SandboxInfo, crIdleTimeout time.Duration, now time.Time) bool` 方法：\n315: - 若 `info.LastActivityAt` 为零值，返回 `false`（不纳入空闲检查）\n316: - 若 `info.Status != \"running\"`，返回 `false`\n317: - 若 `now.After(info.LastActivityAt.Add(crIdleTimeout))`，返回 `true`\n318: - 否则返回 `false`\n319: \n320: #### Scenario: LastActivityAt 为零值时返回 false\n321: \n322: - **GIVEN** `info.LastActivityAt` 为零值\n323: - **WHEN** `isIdleExpired` 被调用\n324: - **THEN** 返回 `false`\n325: \n326: #### Scenario: 非 running 状态返回 false\n327: \n328: - **GIVEN** `info.Status = \"pending\"`，`LastActivityAt` 为 1 小时前\n329: - **WHEN** `isIdleExpired` 被调用\n330: - **THEN** 返回 `false`\n331: \n332: #### Scenario: 超过空闲超时返回 true\n333: \n334: - **GIVEN** `info.Status = \"running\"`，`LastActivityAt` 为 20 分钟前，`crIdleTimeout` 为 15 分钟\n335: - **WHEN** `isIdleExpired` 被调用\n336: - **THEN** 返回 `true`\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: 未超过空闲超时返回 false\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** `info.Status = \"running\"`，`LastActivityAt` 为 10 分钟前，`crIdleTimeout` 为 15 分钟\n341: - **WHEN** `isIdleExpired` 被调用\n342: - **THEN** 返回 `false`\n343: \n344: ---\n345: \n346: ### Requirement: deleteSandbox 方法增强\n347: \n348: The system SHALL 修改 `LifecycleManager.deleteSandbox(ctx, info, reason string)` 方法（签名从两个参数扩展为三个参数，新增 `reason` 参数），在删除 sandbox 后：\n349: 1. 调用 `IncCleanupTotal(reason)` 记录指标（若 MetricsRecorder 非 nil）\n350: 2. 发出结构化删除日志\n351: \n352: #### Scenario: 删除后记录指标和日志\n353: \n354: - **GIVEN** sandbox 因 idle 原因被删除，MetricsRecorder 非 nil\n355: - **WHEN** `deleteSandbox(ctx, info, \"idle\")` 被调用\n356: - **THEN** CR 和 Store 条目被删除\n357: - **AND** `IncCleanupTotal(\"idle\")` 被调用\n358: - **AND** 结构化删除日志被发出\n359: \n360: ---\n361: \n362: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n363: \n364: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n365: 1. `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n366: 2. `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n367: 3. `handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` 行覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n368: 4. 无 goroutine 泄漏（通过 `go test -race` 验证）\n369: 5. 无 `log.Printf` 残留于 `sandbox_lifecycle.go`\n370: \n371: #### Scenario: 编译通过\n372: \n373: - **GIVEN** 所有 GC 增强代码已编写完成\n374: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 执行\n375: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n376: \n377: #### Scenario: 现有生命周期测试不被破坏\n378: \n379: - **GIVEN** 已有的 `sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` 测试用例\n380: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handler/... -v` 执行\n381: - **THEN** 所有现有测试通过（新增字段和方法不影响已有行为）\n382: \n383: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n384: \n385: - **GIVEN** GC 循环涉及 ticker、context、channel 并发操作\n386: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 执行\n387: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n388: \n389: #### Scenario: 无 log.Printf 残留\n390: \n391: - **GIVEN** 所有日志已迁移到 slog\n392: - **WHEN** `grep -n 'log\\.Printf' handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go` 执行\n393: - **THEN** 无匹配结果\n\n(End of file - total 393 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-008: Sandbox GC 定时清理机制 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n增强 `pkg/workloadmanager/handler` 中已有的 `LifecycleManager` GC 循环，新增四项缺失的垃圾回收能力：(1) 基于空闲超时的 sandbox 清理，(2) 孤立 CR（Orphan CR）扫描与删除，(3) 幽灵 Store 条目（Ghost Entry）扫描与清理，(4) GC Prometheus 指标暴露。同时将 GC 路径中的 `log.Printf` 替换为结构化日志 `slog`。本变更是对 AR-005（Sandbox 创建）和 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的补充，确保 sandbox 资源不会因状态不一致而泄漏。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: SandboxInfo 新增 LastActivityAt 字段\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `handler/models.go` 的 `SandboxInfo` 结构体中新增 `LastActivityAt time.Time` 字段，JSON tag 为 `lastActivityAt`。零值表示该 sandbox 不纳入空闲超时检查，回退到 TTL 过期逻辑。Sandbox 创建时 `LastActivityAt` SHALL 初始化为 `CreatedAt`。\n\n#### Scenario: LastActivityAt 初始化为 CreatedAt\n\n- **GIVEN** 新的 sandbox 正在创建\n- **WHEN** `SandboxInfo` 被构造\n- **THEN** `LastActivityAt` 被设置为与 `CreatedAt` 相同的值\n\n#### Scenario: LastActivityAt 为零值时回退到 TTL\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775825953656,"end":1775825953664}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775825954818,"sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","part":{"id":"prt_d7779a3fa001vJ0821uQxkP1c0","messageID":"msg_d7779922d001MjH1hob0AsoMLW","sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5ac0c2e5eeb3499d83cc2f2a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 agentcube 项目构建一个基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块（`pkg/router`），用于将外部 HTTP 请求路由到内部的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 服务实例。该模块将作为 agentcube 系统的流量入口，负责请求分发、负载均衡、服务发现和连接管理。\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In Scope\n10: \n11: 1. **核心反向代理引擎**\n12:    - 基于 `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` 构建可配置的反向代理\n13:    - 支持动态后端发现和路由规则更新\n14:    - 连接池管理和超时控制\n15: \n16: 2. **路由规则管理**\n17:    - 基于路径/Host 的路由匹配\n18:    - 支持通过 Kubernetes CRD（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）动态注册路由\n19:    - 路由优先级和冲突解决机制\n20: \n21: 3. **服务发现集成**\n22:    - 使用 `client-go` 的 Informer 机制监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n23:    - 利用 `SharedInformerFactory` 实现高效的事件驱动更新\n24:    - 通过 `Lister` 接口进行本地缓存查询，减少 API Server 压力\n25: \n26: 4. **负载均衡**\n27:    - 支持 Round-Robin、Least-Connections 等基础策略\n28:    - 健康检查与故障节点剔除\n29: \n30: 5. **中间件支持**\n31:    - 请求/响应日志\n32:    - 请求追踪（Trace ID 注入）\n33:    - 基础认证和限流\n34: \n35: ### Out of Scope\n36: \n37: - TLS 证书管理（由 Ingress Controller 处理）\n38: - 高级流量治理（灰度发布、A/B 测试）\n39: - WebSocket/gRPC 代理支持（后续迭代）\n40: \n41: ## Impact Analysis\n42: \n43: ### Dependencies\n44: \n45: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n46: |------|------|------|\n47: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | 访问 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD | 新增模块依赖，需确保 client-go 版本兼容 |\n48: | `k8s.io/client-go` | Informer/Lister 基础框架 | 间接依赖，版本需与 client-go 生成器一致（v0.34.1） |\n49: | `net/http` + `net/http/httputil` | 反向代理核心 | Go 标准库，无额外依赖 |\n50: \n51: ### Affected Components\n52: \n53: - **API Gateway/Ingress**: 本模块将作为其下游或直接替代部分功能\n54: - **AgentRuntime Controller**: 路由规则变更可能影响控制器的事件处理\n55: - **CodeInterpreter Service**: 新增的路由条目需要与现有服务端口配置对齐\n56: \n57: ### Risk Assessment\n58: \n59: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n60: |------|------|----------|\n61: | Informer 同步延迟导致路由不一致 | 中 | 设置合理的 `defaultResync`，实现降级到 API Server 直查 |\n62: | 后端服务不可用时的错误传播 | 中 | 实现断路器模式和重试机制 |\n63: | 高并发下的连接泄漏 | 低 | 使用 `http.Transport` 连接池配置，定期健康检查 |\n64: \n65: ## Alternatives Considered\n66: \n67: ### 1. 使用现有反向代理（Nginx/Envoy）\n68: \n69: **优点**: 功能成熟、社区支持好、配置丰富  \n70: **缺点**: 需要额外的运维负担、与 Kubernetes CRD 集成需要自定义 Controller、增加系统复杂度  \n71: **决策**: 不采用。agentcube 需要与 CRD 深度集成，自研 Go 模块可以更紧密地利用 client-go 的 Informer 机制。\n72: \n73: ### 2. 基于 Traefik/Contour 等云原生代理扩展\n74: \n75: **优点**: 原生支持 Kubernetes、CRD 路由定义  \n76: **缺点**: 学习曲线陡峭、自定义逻辑需要编写插件（通常为 Go 但受限于插件 API）、调试复杂  \n77: **决策**: 不采用。当前需求相对简单，自研可以更灵活地控制路由逻辑和与 agentcube 其他模块的交互。\n78: \n79: ### 3. 使用 Go 标准库 `httputil.ReverseProxy` 自研（选定方案）\n80: \n81: **优点**: \n82: - 与现有 `pkg/` 模块风格一致\n83: - 直接集成 client-go Informer/Lister 实现动态路由\n84: - 无额外运维负担，部署简单\n85: - 易于扩展和调试\n86: \n87: **缺点**: \n88: - 需要自行实现负载均衡和健康检查\n89: - 高级功能（如限流、熔断）需要额外开发\n90: \n91: **决策**: 采用。符合 agentcube 的技术栈和架构风格，M 规模的实现工作量可控。\n92: \n93: ## Implementation Notes\n94: \n95: ### 核心接口设计\n96: \n97: ```go\n98: type Router interface {\n99:     // AddRoute 动态添加路由规则\n100:     AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n101:     // RemoveRoute 移除路由规则\n102:     RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n103:     // ServeHTTP 实现 http.Handler 接口\n104:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n105: }\n106: \n107: type Backend struct {\n108:     URL      *url.URL\n109:     Weight   int\n110:     Healthy  bool\n111: }\n112: ```\n113: \n114: ### Informer 集成\n115: \n116: ```go\n117: // 使用 SharedInformerFactory 监听 CRD 变更\n118: factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(clientset, 30*time.Second)\n119: agentRuntimeInformer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()\n120: codeInterpreterInformer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters()\n121: \n122: // 注册事件处理器\n123: agentRuntimeInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n124:     AddFunc:    onAgentRuntimeAdded,\n125:     UpdateFunc: onAgentRuntimeUpdated,\n126:     DeleteFunc: onAgentRuntimeDeleted,\n127: })\n128: ```\n129: \n130: ### 目录结构\n131: \n132: ```\n133: pkg/router/\n134: ├── router.go          # Router 接口和核心实现\n135: ├── proxy.go           # ReverseProxy 封装\n136: ├── backend.go         # Backend 管理和健康检查\n137: ├── loadbalancer.go    # 负载均衡策略\n138: ├── middleware.go      # 中间件（日志、追踪、限流）\n139: ├── informer.go        # CRD Informer 集成\n140: ├── config.go          # 配置结构体\n141: └── router_test.go     # 单元测试\n142: ```\n\n(End of file - total 142 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 agentcube 项目构建一个基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块（`pkg/router`），用于将外部 HTTP 请求路由到内部的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 服务实例。该模块将作为 agentcube 系统的流量入口，负责请求分发、负载均衡、服务发现和连接管理。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **核心反向代理引擎**\n   - 基于 `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` 构建可配置的反向代理\n   - 支持动态后端发现和路由规则更新\n   - 连接池管理和超时控制\n\n2. **路由规则管理**\n   - 基于路径/Host 的路由匹配\n   - 支持通过 Kubernetes CRD（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）动态注册路由\n   - 路由优先级和冲突解决机制\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775825954811,"end":1775825954817}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775825955961,"sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","part":{"id":"prt_d7779a8b80015uTEEsTvipKdZK","messageID":"msg_d7779922d001MjH1hob0AsoMLW","sessionID":"ses_28888d3d9ffeu06GNdGttt6Ro5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_768ecb2f3c5d4179ad87f6dc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Session Routing Specification\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: Route HTTP invocation traffic to sandboxes by session: resolve or create sessions via the workload manager, track activity in the store, reverse-proxy to pod endpoints, and sign outbound requests with JWT when targeting sandboxes.\n5: \n6: ## Requirements\n7: \n8: ### Requirement: Session resolution and creation\n9: The system SHALL read session id from request header `x-agentcube-session-id`. When the header is empty, the system SHALL POST to the workload manager to create a sandbox. When non-empty, the system SHALL load `SandboxInfo` from the store by session id.\n10: \n11: #### Scenario: Missing session triggers workload manager create\n12: - **GIVEN** `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` is set and an invocation request has no `x-agentcube-session-id`\n13: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession` runs for `AgentRuntimeKind`\n14: - **THEN** the client POSTs JSON `{\"kind\":\"AgentRuntime\",\"name\":...,\"namespace\":...}` to `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Unknown session returns not found\n17: - **GIVEN** a non-empty session id not present in store\n18: - **WHEN** the store returns `ErrNotFound`\n19: - **THEN** the error maps to `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)` and the HTTP handler responds using API status (typically 404)\n20: \n21: ### Requirement: Workload manager URL and auth token for creates\n22: The system SHALL require environment variable `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` at session manager construction (non-empty). When the file `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` exists and is readable, the system SHALL attach `Authorization: Bearer <trimmed contents>` to create requests.\n23: \n24: #### Scenario: Missing WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL fails startup\n25: - **GIVEN** `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` is unset\n26: - **WHEN** `NewSessionManager` is called\n27: - **THEN** it returns error `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set`\n28: \n29: ### Requirement: Create response validation\n30: The system SHALL accept workload manager HTTP 200 with body `CreateSandboxResponse`; SHALL reject with internal error if `sessionId` in body is empty; SHALL build in-memory `SandboxInfo` with `SandboxID`, `Name` (= `sandboxName`), `SessionID`, `EntryPoints` from the response (other fields may be zero).\n31: \n32: #### Scenario: Non-OK from workload manager\n33: - **GIVEN** workload manager returns HTTP 404\n34: - **WHEN** the session manager handles the response\n35: - **THEN** the error is `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind)`\n36: \n37: ### Requirement: Reverse proxy to sandbox\n38: The system SHALL determine upstream URL from `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` by first matching `path` prefix against the invocation path; if none match, SHALL use the first entry point. The system SHALL build URL by prefixing `protocol` (lowercase) and `://` to `endpoint` when protocol is set and endpoint lacks a scheme. The system SHALL use `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy`, shared `http.Transport` on the proxy, and custom `Director` to set path, host, forwarding headers, and optional JWT.\n39: \n40: #### Scenario: No entry points\n41: - **GIVEN** `EntryPoints` is empty\n42: - **WHEN** upstream is determined\n43: - **THEN** the handler responds 404 JSON `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n44: \n45: ### Requirement: JWT injection for sandbox kinds\n46: For sandbox kinds `Sandbox` and `SandboxClaim`, the system SHALL generate a JWT before proxying and SHALL set `Authorization: Bearer <token>` on the proxied request.\n47: \n48: #### Scenario: Signing failure\n49: - **GIVEN** JWT generation returns an error\n50: - **WHEN** forwarding is attempted\n51: - **THEN** the handler responds 500 with JSON containing `\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"` and `\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"`\n52: \n53: ### Requirement: Forwarding headers and response header\n54: The system SHALL set `X-Forwarded-Host` from the incoming request host, `X-Forwarded-Proto` to `https` when TLS is present else `http`, and `X-Forwarded-For` by appending client IP to any existing values. The system SHALL set response header `x-agentcube-session-id` to the resolved session id on all proxied responses.\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: Path normalization\n57: - **GIVEN** the Gin path param is non-empty and lacks a leading slash\n58: - **WHEN** the director runs\n59: - **THEN** the outbound path is prefixed with `/`\n60: \n61: ### Requirement: Proxy error mapping\n62: The system SHALL map proxy errors containing `connection refused` to 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`, containing `timeout` to 504 `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}`, and other errors to 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`.\n63: \n64: #### Scenario: Downstream connection refused\n65: - **GIVEN** the reverse proxy fails with an error whose message includes `connection refused`\n66: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` runs\n67: - **THEN** status is 502 and error text is `sandbox unreachable`\n68: \n69: ### Requirement: Last-activity updates\n70: The system SHALL call `UpdateSessionLastActivity` with `time.Now()` after successfully resolving the sandbox and again after `forwardToSandbox` returns (twice per successful invoke path). Failures SHALL be logged as warnings only.\n71: \n72: #### Scenario: Store update failure does not block proxy\n73: - **GIVEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` returns an error\n74: - **WHEN** handling continues\n75: - **THEN** the proxy still runs if sandbox resolution succeeded\n76: \n77: ### Requirement: Health endpoints\n78: The system SHALL expose `GET /health/live` returning 200 `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`. The system SHALL expose `GET /health/ready` returning 200 `{\"status\":\"ready\"}` when session manager is non-nil, else 503 with `status` and `error` fields.\n79: \n80: #### Scenario: Ready depends on session manager\n81: - **GIVEN** `sessionManager` is nil\n82: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` is served\n83: - **THEN** status is 503 and body includes `\"error\":\"session manager not available\"`\n84: \n85: ### Requirement: Concurrency limiting\n86: The system SHALL apply a semaphore middleware to `/v1/*` routes with capacity `MaxConcurrentRequests` (default 1000 when config value ≤ 0). When no slot is available, the system SHALL respond 429 JSON `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}` and abort.\n87: \n88: #### Scenario: Default limit when zero in config\n89: - **GIVEN** `NewServer` receives `MaxConcurrentRequests` 0\n90: - **WHEN** the server is constructed\n91: - **THEN** the effective limit is set to 1000 before route registration\n92: \n93: ### Requirement: Invocation route surface\n94: The system SHALL register GET and POST for `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` and for `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path`, with Gin logger, recovery, and concurrency middleware on the `/v1` group only.\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: Kind passed to session lookup\n97: - **GIVEN** agent-runtime invocation\n98: - **WHEN** `handleInvoke` runs\n99: - **THEN** kind argument is `AgentRuntime` (`types.AgentRuntimeKind`)\n100: \n101: ### Requirement: HTTP server behavior\n102: The system SHALL serve with `h2c` and `http2.Server`, `ReadTimeout` 30s, `IdleTimeout` 90s; on context cancel SHALL shutdown within 10s. Optional TLS SHALL require both cert and key paths.\n103: \n104: #### Scenario: TLS misconfiguration\n105: - **GIVEN** `EnableTLS` true and empty cert path\n106: - **WHEN** `Start` runs\n107: - **THEN** it returns error stating cert/key not provided\n108: \n109: ### Requirement: Identity secret bootstrap for JWT\n110: On server creation the system SHALL construct `JWTManager`, call `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret`, and fail server creation if that returns error (except in-cluster skip path returns nil when not in cluster).\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: In-cluster secret creation\n113: - **GIVEN** in-cluster config succeeds and secret does not exist\n114: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret` runs\n115: - **THEN** it creates opaque secret `picod-router-identity` in namespace from `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` or `default` with keys `private.pem` and `public.pem`\n\n(End of file - total 115 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Session Routing Specification\n\n## Purpose\nRoute HTTP invocation traffic to sandboxes by session: resolve or create sessions via the workload manager, track activity in the store, reverse-proxy to pod endpoints, and sign outbound requests with JWT when targeting sandboxes.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Session resolution and creation\nThe system SHALL read session id from request header `x-agentcube-session-id`. When the header is empty, the system SHALL POST to the workload manager to create a sandbox. When non-empty, the system SHALL load `SandboxInfo` from the store by session id.\n\n#### Scenario: Missing session triggers workload manager create\n- **GIVEN** `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` is set and an invocation request has no `x-agentcube-session-id`\n- **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession` runs for `AgentRuntimeKind`\n- **THEN** the client POSTs JSON `{\"kind\":\"AgentRuntime\",\"name\":...,\"namespace\":...}` to `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`\n\n#### Scenario: Unknown session returns not found\n- **GIVEN** a non-empty session id not present in store\n- **WHEN** the store returns `ErrNotFound`\n- **THEN** the error maps to `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)` and the HTTP handler responds using API status (typically 404)\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/spec.md","time":{"start":1775825955953,"end":1775825955959}}}}
